華奧會：尊重隱私 過去未公布涉禁藥選手名單 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201903270294.aspx |language=zh-tw |author=龍柏安 |publisher=中央社 |date=2019-03-27 |accessdate=2019-03-27 |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327112841/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201903270294.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

